criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Women with singleton pregnancy;

          -  Regular antenatal examination from the first trimester;

          -  Give birth in the university hospital (The 1st affiliated hospital of Sun Yat-sen
             University)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Younger than 18 years old;

          -  Older than 40 years old;

          -  Multiple pregnancy;

          -  Diagnosed DM before pregnancy;

          -  Complicated with other diseases such as hypertension, eclampsia, thyroid diseases,
             etc.;

          -  Taking any drug that affect glucose and lipid metabolism and insulin sensitivity.
